  {
    "text": "I'll meet you back at the bridge.",
    "start": 33.825,
    "duration": 1.377
  },
  {
    "text": "- Yay!\n- Pawsome.",
    "start": 35.285,
    "duration": 1.085
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know how much longer it'll hold.",
