  {
    "text": "We don't have to.\nI'm gonna go through them.",
    "start": 98.39,
    "duration": 2.711
  },
  {
    "text": "Rubble, lift me up\nas high as you can, please.",
    "start": 101.852,
    "duration": 2.669
  },
  {
    "text": "Mighty and small, I'll give it my all!",
    "start": 107.858,
    "duration": 2.711
  },
  {
    "text": "- Whoa.\n- Awesome.",
    "start": 116.867,
    "duration": 2.586
  },
  {
    "text": "So bright and twinkly!",
    "start": 120.412,
    "duration": 1.96
